PrecisAuthority for the NATIONAL CAPITAL COMMISSION (a) to lease the lands and premises comprising CAMP FORTUNE, a ski and recreational facility located in Gatineau Park, to GRAND BEACH SKI CORPORATION, for a term of up to fifty years, and (b) to grant them an attendant easement for the purposes of access to lake Fortune in order to regulate the water flow for snow-making purposes.
